wizardry.spell.effect_anti_gravity_well.name=Antigravity Well
wizardry.spell.effect_anti_gravity_well.desc=Repulses all entities around the target.
wizardry.spell.effect_anti_gravity_well.desc.area=Pushes away all entities within <AREA> blocks and farther than 2 blocks from the center.
wizardry.spell.effect_anti_gravity_well.desc.potency=Pushes entities in with with a force dependent on <POTENCY>.
wizardry.spell.effect_anti_gravity_well.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_backup.name=Reinforcements
wizardry.spell.effect_backup.desc=Summons undead mobs to aid in battle.
wizardry.spell.effect_backup.desc.duration=Summoned zombies last <DURATION> seconds.
wizardry.spell.effect_break.name=Break
wizardry.spell.effect_break.desc=Breaks blocks and damages armor.
wizardry.spell.effect_break.desc.area=Breaks up to <AREA> blocks. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_break.desc.potency=Breaks blocks with up to <POTENCY> hardness. Does <POTENCY> damage to a target's armor.
wizardry.spell.effect_burn.name=Burn
wizardry.spell.effect_burn.desc=Ignites the target block or entity.
wizardry.spell.effect_burn.desc.area=Lights all blocks within <AREA> blocks on fire. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_burn.desc.duration=Lights target entity on fire for <DURATION> seconds. No effect on blocks.
wizardry.spell.effect_crasher_fall.name=Crashing Fall
wizardry.spell.effect_crasher_fall.desc=Distribute some of the target's impact damage into any nearby entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_crasher_fall.desc.range=<RANGE> increases area checked for nearby entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_crasher_fall.desc.duration=Effect lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_extract.name=Extract
wizardry.spell.effect_extract.desc=Extracts items from the target entity or block with an inventory. Respects locked containers.
wizardry.spell.effect_extract.desc.duration=The time it takes the item to delay pickup by the nearest entity.
wizardry.spell.effect_extract.desc.potency=Less than quarter power searches inventory back to front, less than half searches front to back (hotbar first), more than that removes baubles first, then armor, then inventory front to back.
wizardry.spell.effect_frost.name=Frost
wizardry.spell.effect_frost.desc=Makes opponents slip and slide as if on ice, extinguishes fires, cools liquids, and causes snowfall.
wizardry.spell.effect_frost.desc.area=Extinguishes fires, cools liquids, and places snow within <AREA> blocks of the target. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_frost.desc.duration=Makes opponents slippery for half a second per point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_gravity_well.name=Gravity Well
wizardry.spell.effect_gravity_well.desc=Draws in all entities around the target.
wizardry.spell.effect_gravity_well.desc.area=Pulls in all entities within <AREA> blocks and farther than 2 blocks from the center.
wizardry.spell.effect_gravity_well.desc.potency=Pulls entities in with with a force dependent on <POTENCY>.
wizardry.spell.effect_gravity_well.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_leap.name=Leap
wizardry.spell.effect_leap.desc=Thrusts you upwards and forwards.
wizardry.spell.effect_leap.desc.potency=Can jump in the air once for every 10 points of <POTENCY>. Divides fall distance by 1 + <POTENCY>/8, rounded up.
wizardry.spell.effect_leech.name=Leech
wizardry.spell.effect_leech.desc=Will deal magic damage to a target. If that target dies, you get some of their mana into yourself.
wizardry.spell.effect_leech.desc.potency=Does a point of magic damage (1 heart) per point of <POTENCY>.
wizardry.spell.effect_light.name=Illumination
wizardry.spell.effect_light.desc=Places a magical light source at the target location.
wizardry.spell.effect_lightning.name=Lightning
wizardry.spell.effect_lightning.desc=Shoot a lightning bolt that shocks and burns everything in its path. Functions slightly differently depending on the previous Shape in the spell.
wizardry.spell.effect_lightning.desc.range=The lightning bolt and its offshoots can be up to <RANGE> blocks long.
wizardry.spell.effect_lightning.desc.potency=Deals <POTENCY> lightning damage.
wizardry.spell.effect_lightning.desc.duration=Entities hit are ignited for <DURATION> seconds.
wizardry.spell.effect_low_gravity.name=Low Gravity
wizardry.spell.effect_low_gravity.desc=The target becomes half their weight, jumping high and floating down.
wizardry.spell.effect_low_gravity.desc.potency=Jump height increased and fall damage decreased per point of <POTENCY>.
wizardry.spell.effect_low_gravity.desc.duration=The effect lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_phase.name=Phase
wizardry.spell.effect_phase.desc=The target becomes incorporeal, phasing through blocks temporarily. If cast on blocks, turns an area of blocks incorporeal instead.
wizardry.spell.effect_phase.desc.duration=The effect lasts for <DURATION> seconds.
wizardry.spell.effect_phase.desc.area=Affects all blocks within <AREA> blocks of the target block. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_phase.desc.range=Phase effect reaches <RANGE> blocks past the target block. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_place.name=Place
wizardry.spell.effect_place.desc=Places the selected block.
wizardry.spell.effect_place.desc.area=Can place blocks in up to <AREA> positions at once.
wizardry.spell.effect_substitution.name=Substitute
wizardry.spell.effect_substitution.desc=Swaps the caster's position with that of the target. Blocks work similarly.
wizardry.spell.effect_substitution.desc.area=Can swap up to <AREA> blocks at once. No effect on entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_telekinesis.name=Telekinesis
wizardry.spell.effect_telekinesis.desc=Levitates blocks and entities.
wizardry.spell.effect_telekinesis.desc.area=Grabs all entities and items within <AREA> blocks of the center.
wizardry.spell.effect_thrive.name=Thrive
wizardry.spell.effect_thrive.desc=Heals entities and speeds growth.
wizardry.spell.effect_thrive.desc.potency=Entities are healed for 1/4 heart per point of <POTENCY>. No effect on blocks.
wizardry.spell.effect_time_slow.name=Time Slow
wizardry.spell.effect_time_slow.desc=Dilates an entity's time. Can suspend their time completely.
wizardry.spell.effect_time_slow.desc.potency=Slows down an entity to 1/<POTENCY> normal time.
wizardry.spell.effect_time_slow.desc.duration=Effect lasts half a second per point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_time_lock.name=Time Lock
wizardry.spell.effect_time_lock.desc=Once the spell expires, reverts the target block or entity to its previous state when the spell was cast.
wizardry.spell.effect_time_lock.desc.duration=Effect lasts half a second per point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_vanish.name=Vanish
wizardry.spell.effect_vanish.desc=The target can't see anyone when they're moving, but when they're still, they're invisible.
wizardry.spell.effect_vanish.desc.duration=Effect lasts for <DURATION> seconds.
wizardry.spell.effect_zoom.name=Zoom
wizardry.spell.effect_zoom.desc=Zoom directly to the targeted position.
wizardry.spell.effect_zoom.desc.range=Instantly moves you up to <RANGE> blocks.
wizardry.spell.effect_poison_cloud.name=Poison Cloud
wizardry.spell.effect_poison_cloud.desc=Create a poisonous cloud of gas
wizardry.spell.effect_poison_cloud.desc.potency=Every 3 points of <POTENCY> increases the level of poison by 1. Potency above 3 will also inflict nausea.
wizardry.spell.effect_poison_cloud.desc.area=Will inflict poison on each entity within <AREA> blocks.
wizardry.spell.effect_poison_cloud.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_decay.name=Decay
wizardry.spell.effect_decay.desc=Causes the target to decay, slowing and withering them.
wizardry.spell.effect_decay.desc.potency=Every 5 points of <POTENCY> increases the level of slowness and wither by 1.
wizardry.spell.effect_decay.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_grace.name=Grace
wizardry.spell.effect_grace.desc=Grants increased movement speed until the next attack, which will automatically crit.
wizardry.spell.effect_grace.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>, until an attack is made.
wizardry.spell.effect_shatter.name=Shatter
wizardry.spell.effect_shatter.desc=Deals damage to a target, increased for each level of slowness or frost on them.
wizardry.spell.effect_shatter.desc.potency=Deals a base damage of <POTENCY>/2, increased by 50% per level of slowness or frost.
wizardry.spell.effect_sonic.name=Sonic Scream
wizardry.spell.effect_sonic.desc=Deals damage to a target. If they die from this, they explode, dealing the same damage to all entities in an area.
wizardry.spell.effect_sonic.desc.potency=Deals <POTENCY>/2 damage.
wizardry.spell.effect_sonic.desc.area=Secondary explosion deals damage to all entities within <AREA>/2 blocks.
wizardry.spell.effect_suffocate.name=Suffocate
wizardry.spell.effect_suffocate.desc=Causes the target to suffocate as if they had run out of air.
wizardry.spell.effect_suffocate.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.
wizardry.spell.effect_bouncing.name=Bouncing
wizardry.spell.effect_bouncing.desc=Entities hit by this spell will bounce on everything they fall on. Blocks hit will also become bouncy.
wizardry.spell.effect_bouncing.desc.duration=Lasts half a second for each point of <DURATION>.

wizardry.spell.event_collide_block.name=On Block Collision
wizardry.spell.event_collide_block.desc=This event triggers when the spell collides with a block. Place directly before an effect to cause it to only affect blocks.
wizardry.spell.event_collide_entity.name=On Entity Collision
wizardry.spell.event_collide_entity.desc=This event triggers when the spell collides with an entity. Place directly before an effect to cause it to only affect entities.

wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_range.name=Extend Range
wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_range.desc=Lengthens the range of reach of the spell.
wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_range.short=+ Range
wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_time.name=Extend Effect
wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_time.desc=Extends the length of time the spell lasts.
wizardry.spell.modifier_extend_time.short=+ Time
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_aoe.name=Increase Area
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_aoe.desc=Increases the spell's area of effect.
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_aoe.short=+ Area
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_potency.name=Increase Power
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_potency.desc=Amplifies a spell's strength.
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_potency.short=+ Power
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_speed.name=Increase Speed
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_speed.desc=Increases the velocity of the spell, as with projectiles.
wizardry.spell.modifier_increase_speed.short=+ Speed

wizardry.spell.shape_beam.name=Beam
wizardry.spell.shape_beam.desc=The spell will affect a beam coming from the caster.
wizardry.spell.shape_beam.desc.range=Traces a line up to <RANGE> blocks long.
wizardry.spell.shape_beam.desc.potency=Gains <POTENCY> points per cast, runs subsequent spell components after reaching 10 points.
wizardry.spell.shape_cone.name=Arc
wizardry.spell.shape_cone.desc=The spell will affect an arc in front of the caster.
wizardry.spell.shape_cone.desc.range=Maximum distance and spread increased per point of <RANGE>.
wizardry.spell.shape_cone.desc.potency=Spell fires along <POTENCY> random lines within the cone's spread.
wizardry.spell.shape_projectile.name=Projectile
wizardry.spell.shape_projectile.desc=The spell will be a projectile, launched from the caster.
wizardry.spell.shape_projectile.desc.range=The projectile will travel up to 2*<RANGE> blocks before casting subsequent components.
wizardry.spell.shape_projectile.desc.speed=The projectile will travel <SPEED> blocks per second.
wizardry.spell.shape_self.name=Self
wizardry.spell.shape_self.desc=The spell will affect the caster directly.
wizardry.spell.shape_touch.name=Touch
wizardry.spell.shape_touch.desc=The spell will affect what the caster is touching.
wizardry.spell.shape_zone.name=Zone
wizardry.spell.shape_zone.desc=The spell will be a circular area, and cast itself persistently.
wizardry.spell.shape_zone.desc.area=Casts subsequent components on entities and blocks within <AREA> blocks of the center, horizontally.
wizardry.spell.shape_zone.desc.potency=Gains <POTENCY> points per cast, runs subsequent spell components after reaching 20 points.
